longBusinessSummary: Fingerprint Cards AB (publ), a biometrics company, engages in the development, production, and marketing of biometric systems and technologies in Sweden, France, Hong Kong, China, the United States, and internationally. The company develops biometric systems comprising sensors, microcontrollers, algorithms, software, and packaging technologies for smartphones, PCs, tablets, smart cards, door locks, authentication keys, vehicles, payment cards, internet of things, and automotive industry. It sells its products through distributors and resellers. Fingerprint Cards AB (publ) was incorporated in 1971 and is headquartered in Gothenburg, Sweden.
